AWS SNS Mobile push
	Create a Topic for Mobile Push Messages
	Add Subscriber to the Topic. Each subscriber would be a device/app endpoint
	
	Send Mobile Push messages to Topic
	All subscribers to the Topic receive the message on the device
	
	Send Mobile Push message to specific app/device endpoint
	App/Device endpoint receives the message on the app/device
	

AWS SNS Web hooks
	Create a Topic for Web hooks
	Add Subscriber to the Topic. Each subscriber would be a Http/s endpoint
	
	Send  messages to Topic
	All subscribers to the Topic receive the message on the http/s endpoint
	
	Send message to specific http/s endpoint
	http/s endpoint receives the message 
	


	

	
In-browser App Notifications/icon notifications(SSE)
====================================================

https://dev.to/4shub/building-with-server-sent-events-13j
https://www.digitalocean.com/community/tutorials/nodejs-server-sent-events-build-realtime-app

Can use AWS SNS Topic with channel as HTTP Endpoint

	
	Server Sent Events (SSE)
	Register the app on a specific endpoint
	store the subscription in the data store
	
	Send messages to all the connected client/users
	Fetch the subscription(s) from the data store
	Send a message to each of the subscription 
	

		

